{"tid":1702904,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我都係想為香港姐, 但家人反對","createTime":"2019-11-10T03:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T21:21:14.000Z","uid":35361,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7cdcae9ea908ea91197cca1c3f147747482e0e","tid":1702904,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:55:22.000Z","msg":"本身我地一家人都係黃  平時大家都為香港出心出力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時佢地係返工既時候 見到facebook d 三罷post 都會盡全力去比like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又會係林鄭直播果d post 搏盡咁比嬲嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又會聽願榮光歸香港 Do You Hear the People Sing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期六日通常見到十點就冇港鐵 一般就會留係屋企睇住立場直播 支援手足們發夢開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁今日我地如常地係屋企支持手足 盡全力係facebook比like比心比嬲嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但因為我部機真係太慢(用緊samsung S5), 有時想快d幫手推下連登行動post都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就同老豆講比錢我換S10 可以更快更有效地推post比like撐香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知佢發老皮 話我部S5仲未壞 做咩要換機 仲一手推跌左我地個吉野家外賣lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家係富臨排緊買飯  究竟食叉雞 / 叉鴨好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da6438babca5824a3b8e870046af3d253931cc0","tid":1702904,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c949be85907620337b5c1f3c116256c9023f798","tid":1702904,"uid":211814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"Are u ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,small brain"},{"pid":"7e111a01cfae82b3bf69cbc27fea72a01b60fd34","tid":1702904,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c949be85907620337b5c1f3c116256c9023f798","tid":1702904,"uid":211814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"Are u ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,small brain"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565315cb7e02f50d4846c8e35ee849c0df36cdda","tid":1702904,"uid":114347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"偽黃絲"},{"pid":"c8913a462683d2b2954c6c388f59dd31cf0e730b","tid":1702904,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"咁你老豆有真係窮酸左啲嘅<br />\n<br />\n一部電話都無錢換俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2105841638e0b394ae121b8e39e42126dd3ba2b2","tid":1702904,"uid":311796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:06:51.000Z","msg":"吉野家 富臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},